            </p>
            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Targets hyperpigmentation &amp; dullness</li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Breakouts &amp; post-inflammatory marks</li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Variable downtime by strength</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="md:col-span-7">
            <a href="/contact-us/" class="group block rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-neutral-100 ring-1 ring-neutral-200">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none"><path d="M9 3h6l1 3H8l1-3zM7 21h10M6 14h12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Which peel is right for me?</h3>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600">Personalized plan by indication &amp; season</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3 text-sm underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-300 text-neutral-800 group-hover:decoration-neutral-700">Request consult →</div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container"><div class="h-px bg-neutral-200"></div></div>

    <!-- Specialty Facials -->
    <section id="facials" class="scroll-mt-28 py-12 sm:py-14">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="md:col-span-5">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Specialty Facials</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
              Session-by-session customization using enzymes, gentle acids, masks and devices to keep
              barrier health front and center.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Hydration &amp; radiance protocols</li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Redness-friendly options</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="md:col-span-7">
            <a href="/contact-us/" class="group block rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-neutral-100 ring-1 ring-neutral-200">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none"><path d="M5 7h14M7 12h10M9 17h6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Build your facial plan</h3>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600">Choose focus, cadence &amp; add-ons</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3 text-sm underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-300 text-neutral-800 group-hover:decoration-neutral-700">Start here →</div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container"><div class="h-px bg-neutral-200"></div></div>

    <!-- Acne Programs -->
    <section id="acne-programs" class="scroll-mt-28 py-12 sm:py-14">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="md:col-span-5">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Acne Programs</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
              Face Reality® Boot Camp and tailored anti-acne roadmaps—routine design, product pairing, and
              check-ins to keep you on track.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Clear goals &amp; progress tracking</li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Product education &amp; skin cycling</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="md:col-span-7">
            <a href="/contact-us/" class="group block rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-neutral-100 ring-1 ring-neutral-200">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none"><path d="M12 2v6m0 8v6M2 12h6m8 0h6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Face Reality® &amp; custom plans</h3>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600">Intake, cadence &amp; check-ins</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3 text-sm underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-300 text-neutral-800 group-hover:decoration-neutral-700">Enroll →</div>
