            </p>
            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Soft glow, smoother makeup</li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>Pairs well with facials &amp; peels</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="md:col-span-7">
            <a href="/contact-us/" class="group block rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-neutral-100 ring-1 ring-neutral-200">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none"><path d="M5 7h14M6 12h12M7 17h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Dermaplaning &amp; Enzyme options</h3>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600">Which combo fits your skin today</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3 text-sm underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-300 text-neutral-800 group-hover:decoration-neutral-700">Ask a provider →</div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Short FAQ -->
    <section class="py-12 sm:py-14 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How many microneedling sessions will I need?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
